{"tid":891061,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"顛覆商業認知！iu無打歌下竟七度奪冠","createTime":"2018-11-05T21:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T12:05:56.000Z","uid":34643,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"138ca1ed380f5cbd583c066c83a0ae1209895160","tid":891061,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T21:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_3e8f5225ce708f941ce9a5eda8b9d3e8/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-04/110906-673070.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_3e8f5225ce708f941ce9a5eda8b9d3e8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-04%2F110906-673070.png&h=a9fd2972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在歌手或團體各出奇招、從各種通路下手努力激發銷量的時代，IU 以別出心裁的作品重新證明了音樂本身的價值！<br />\n<br />\n昨天（4 日）SBS 停播一周的《人氣歌謠》經由官網公布了冠軍得主，IU 憑著出道十週年特別單曲 &ldquo;BBIBBI&rdquo; 登上 11 月首週的寶座，而這同時也是她這次發行新歌後連續第三週在本節目奪冠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c55549fd1d0a5e6544726f99bdc36efc/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-04/110906-673069.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c55549fd1d0a5e6544726f99bdc36efc%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-04%2F110906-673069.png&h=7b4088db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n距離 &ldquo;BBIBBI&rdquo; 發行的 10 月 10 日已經過了近一個月，這段期間 IU 完全沒有透過任何音樂節目進行宣傳，只埋頭準備日前開跑的亞洲巡迴演唱會，但是她到目前為止已經在音樂節目上七度奪冠，其中在 MBC 的《Show! 音樂中心》和 SBS 的《人氣歌謠》都寫下了蟬聯三週冠軍的亮眼成績。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_733f8c0c263154ebac0ea58224c1379e/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-04/110906-673072.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_733f8c0c263154ebac0ea58224c1379e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-04%2F110906-673072.jpg&h=e66413b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2ca49736c31eed2769ff83ba3618ffee/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-04/110906-673074.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2ca49736c31eed2769ff83ba3618ffee%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-04%2F110906-673074.png&h=f5f742fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不僅如此，Gaon Chart 日前公布今年第 43 週 (10/21~10/27) 的排行榜，IU 也在數位、下載和串流播放三榜上拿下冠軍。另一方面，IU 昨天也終於首度公開 &quot;BBIBBI&quot; 的舞蹈練習現場，率性俏皮的動作感覺很快就會掀起模仿潮啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hngml3y2Rq8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhngml3y2Rq8&d=Jq7s48F6jj01KZUe6UZzWL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=08cef3e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hngml3y2Rq8</a>"},{"pid":"80bf54d4798264b8773f0c5550f773bf69b1042f","tid":891061,"uid":34643,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T21:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DpLtrZsW0AElOAo.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDpLtrZsW0AElOAo.jpg%3Aorig&h=fea21482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/1de3972ad323fd7de81ffcbd374dc0fb/tumblr_pgl6wqYRbd1rlzlwyo1_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F1de3972ad323fd7de81ffcbd374dc0fb%2Ftumblr_pgl6wqYRbd1rlzlwyo1_1280.jpg&h=8adf7cdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50122464a916a1918caadba1f8d630d3128506e5","tid":891061,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T21:30:15.000Z","msg":"Iu bb"},{"pid":"67fc71d19ce5f5c4f37f8efe7d1271cc27b92d79","tid":891061,"uid":34643,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"50122464a916a1918caadba1f8d630d3128506e5","tid":891061,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T21:30:15.000Z","msg":"Iu bb"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T21:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CE3VFYj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCE3VFYj.jpg&h=f19c7f92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35cfc5b65cb08bddc455735b4774ef8f57a04708","tid":891061,"uid":34584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT